# DocuNotes Features and Functionality

## Core Features

### Document Processing
- Support for `.docx` file format
- In-browser file processing using JSZip
- Extraction of comments and annotations
- Privacy-focused (no server uploads)

### User Interface
- Drag-and-drop file upload
- Table view of extracted comments
- Excel export functionality
- Modern, responsive design

### Data Management
- Comment extraction and parsing
- Data transformation and formatting
- Excel file generation
- Error handling and validation

